Last night I couldn’t fall asleep for shit. Worried about so much and I woke up today hitting TOP 40 @billboard CHARTS!!!!! This is the first time my OWN song hit this kind of milestone. It’s wild ♥️♥️♥️
@maxineashley gets in her bag for a live performance of “Somebody Else” 🔥❤️ Full video link in bio

Let me just break it down for ya real quick! 

In just a few months we had planned to release “Somebody else” as soon I flew back to LA. I had 2 weeks to prep for the video, I was so stressed out I got pink eye in both my eyes. Thank god EVERY single person on set was chill, professional and talented. It took months for me to even be satisfied with the final video (I think it took like 10 edits….sorry lol) Shout out to @michaelrainin for his patience fr lol. 

Within those months I moved to an apartment complex with neighbors who were discriminating against me and my friends. They made my living environment fucking HELL!!! They didn’t allow me to make music. I had to pack up and leave to then find out, a week later I’m performing MADISON SQUARE GARDEN!! It was bittersweet not knowing where I was gonna live to then performing one of the biggest stages in NYC, WHERE IM FROM. 

SO then BOOM the video and song drops. I expect nothing because I’ve been doing this for so long and it’s been YEARS since I’ve released anything. I was so nervous and doubting my every move. I’ve had people make fun of me and pray on my downfall, but my team @jbrcreativegroup MADE SURE to never let that happen. 

I’m skipping over a lot because I don’t want to make this too long… but damn. Look at where we are now. TOP 40 on @billboardcharts 

From having to force myself to leave an apartment, to Madison square garden, to my song being on the radio, to a breakup, to then getting on top 40. 

Life is truly ying and yang. I can’t wait to see where else this goes!!
Every listen is appreciated, every release is a milestone. It’s a blessing to have such loyal listeners even after 3 years of silence, love ya. More coming soon!!♥️♥️♥️

Thank you @billboard for the official write up!! So cool to see that people are actually enjoying the song♥️
@billboardcharts let’s see how far the songs climbs🤞🏼💓

Shoutout to all the radio stations, DJs and Program Directors who made my first West Coast Promo Tour so special! ♥️ (wish I could've fit you all into this video)

Me and my team at @JBRcreativegroup appreciate all the support. Can't wait to see you all again soon 🤞🏽
Life is lifing

social_posts.post_text: Performing at @thegarden with @realblackcoffee was amazing and I’m glad it was documented !

Went on a 2 week radio promo tour and met amazing people! I got to sit down with @siriusxmtheheat and so much more to talk about my new single. 
Towards the end I got sick with the flu and have been later out in bed for a week, within that week I found out my city (NYC) is playing my song on the radio!!!! @1035ktu and so much more. 
Thank you so much to everyone I came across it was so special but also 🖕🏼 to who got me sick lmaooo.
